Package me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.api

Class BlockInfoConfig

java.lang.Object
me.mrCookieSlime.CSCoreLibPlugin.Configuration.Config
me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.api.BlockInfoConfig
public class BlockInfoConfig extends Config
This class is used to speed up parsing of a JsonObject that is stored at a given Location.

This simply utilises a HashMap to cache the data and then provides the same getters as a normal Config.

Author:
creator3
